  <title>Basic instructions</title>

<section id="start">
  <title>Start a new game</title>

  <p>Press the <gui style="button">New Game</gui> button in the header bar to start a new
  game when being in a game.</p>
  <p>Press the <gui style="button">Play Again</gui> button when you have finished a game.</p>

</section>

<section id="pause">
  <title>Pause and resume your game</title>

  <p>Press the <gui style="button">Pause</gui> button in the header bar to pause your game.
  You can resume your game by pressing the <gui style="button">Resume</gui> button.</p>

</section>

<section id="quit">
  <title>Quit <app>Nibbles</app></title>

  <p>Press the <gui style="button">тип</gui> button in the header bar or press
  <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Q</key></keyseq> to quit <app>Nibbles</app>
  at any time.</p>

</section>

